Michelle Jenneke: Cyrus Hostetler attempts jiggle at Nitro Athletics - Yahoo7 Thereâ€™s only one Michelle Jenneke, right? Close American javelin star does the Jenneke jiggle UP NEXT VIDEO American javelin star does the Jenneke jiggle. Source: Channel 7 American javelin star does the Jenneke jiggle 
The famous Aussie hurdler and her infamous jiggling pre-race routine is known around the world. 
But at Nitro Athletics overnight one other athlete tried to get in on a bit of that action and hopefully adoration. Who wears it better? Pic: Channel 7 and Getty 
American javelin thrower Cyrus Hostetler was taking part, threw very long, but slightly wide before playing it up to the cameras doing his best Jenneke impersonation. 
It might not catch on around the world like Jenneke but points for the attempt and enthusiasm.
